---
const CTA_PRIMARY = "View Projects";
const CTA_SECONDARY = "Download CV";
---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    {/* subtle top grid glow */}
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 -top-10 h-56 opacity-60 [mask-image:linear-gradient(180deg,white,transparent)]">
        <div class="h-full w-full bg-[repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,#0f131b_0_2px,transparent_2px_24px)]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container pt-16 md:pt-24 pb-14 md:pb-20">
        <div class="grid gap-10 md:gap-12 md:grid-cols-12 items-center">
            {/* LEFT */}
            <div class="md:col-span-7">
                <p class="text-sm text-accent-300/90 font-medium">
                    Hey there <span class="inline-block wave origin-[70%_70%]">üëãüèª</span>
                </p>

                <h1 class="mt-3 font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[clamp(2.25rem,4.5vw,3.5rem)] leading-[1.1]">
                    I‚Äôm Brad
                </h1>

                <h2 class="mt-2 font-bold tracking-tight text-[clamp(1.25rem,2.2vw,1.75rem)] bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-accent-400">
                    HPC dev, C++/Java enjoyer, and builder of fast things.
                </h2>

                <p class="mt-5 md:mt-6 max-w-2xl text-[0.98rem] leading-relaxed text-zinc-300">
                    I design and ship high-performance systems across HPC clusters, backend services,
                    and developer tools that scale efficiently and make engineers‚Äô lives easier.
                </p>

                {/* CTAs */}
                <div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                    <a href="#projects"
                       class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-accent-500 text-black px-4 py-2.5 font-semibold shadow-soft hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,.35)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition">
                        {CTA_PRIMARY}
                    </a>
                    <a href="/Documents/Bnorthern25_resume.pdf"
                       class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl border border-white/15 px-4 py-2.5 font-semibold text-zinc-100/90 hover:text-zinc-100 hover:border-accent-400/60 transition">
                        {CTA_SECONDARY}
                    </a>
                </div>

                {/* Tech chips (optional but adds texture) */}
                <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    {["OpenMP / OpenMPI","Spring Boot","PostgreSQL","Linux ‚Ä¢ Arch/RHEL/SUSE"].map((b) => (
                            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-zinc-300 border border-white/10 bg-[#0f131b]">
              {b}
            </span>
                    ))}
                </div>
            </div>

            {/* RIGHT: code card */}
            <div class="md:col-span-12 mt-6">
                <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#10131a]/90 p-5 overflow-x-auto">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-1 mb-3">
                        <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></span>
                        <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></span>
                        <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
                    </div>
                    <pre class="text-sm md:text-base font-mono leading-relaxed text-zinc-200">
$ cat kitpp/README.md
A reusable C++ utility library for real work.
- Built for clusters
- Zero fluff, just speed
- Batteries included (sane defaults)
    </pre>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
